targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  eventid,
  description,
  datentime
FROM
  $table
WHERE
  eventid = '$eventid'
  AND machine = '$machine'
ORDER BY datentime

SELECT
  $__timeEpoch(datentime),
  count as value,
  eventid as metric
FROM
  $table
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(datentime)
  AND
  machine = '$machine'
  AND
  count < $count
ORDER BY
  datentime ASC
